[{"Code":"en","Title":"PayLater channels","Slug":"paylater-channels","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mc3bh5ns-cyul9t-039\">PayLater<span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"color:rgb(24, 24, 27);background:rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family:Inter;font-size:16px;font-weight:300;text-transform:none;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;float:none;display:inline !important;\"><span type=\"spanNode\">&nbsp;allows </span>end users to accept payments via credits provided by our payment partners. End users will be redirected to complete a one-time payment flow. You can learn how to integrate with PayLater channels </span><a href=\"https://archive.developers.xendit.co/api-reference/#paylater\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">here</a><span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"color:rgb(24, 24, 27);background:rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family:Inter;font-size:16px;font-weight:300;text-transform:none;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;float:none;display:inline !important;\">.</span></p><p data-block-id=\"mc3bggkm-pln7f7-038\"></p>","SeoTitle":"PayLater channels","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Channel Paylater","Slug":"paylater-channels","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mcs2yla6-j9qowm-203\"><strong>Paylater</strong><span style=\"color:rgb(24, 24, 27);background:rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family:Inter;font-size:16px;font-weight:300;text-transform:none;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;display:inline !important;float:none;\" type=\"spanMark\"><span type=\"spanNode\"> memungkinkan </span>pengguna akhir untuk menerima pembayaran melalui kredit yang disediakan oleh mitra pembayaran kami. Pengguna akhir akan diarahkan untuk menyelesaikan alur pembayaran satu kali. Anda dapat mempelajari cara berintegrasi dengan saluran paylater </span><a href=\"https://archive.developers.xendit.co/api-reference/#paylater\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">di sini</a><span style=\"color:rgb(24, 24, 27);background:rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family:Inter;font-size:16px;font-weight:300;text-transform:none;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;display:inline !important;float:none;\" type=\"spanMark\">.</span></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs2yla8-k3xs5k-204\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Channel Paylater","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"ช่องทาง Paylater","Slug":"paylater-channels","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"mc3bh5ns-cyul9t-039\"><strong>Paylater</strong><span style=\"color:rgb(24, 24, 27);background:rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family:Inter;font-size:16px;font-weight:300;text-transform:none;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:nor